{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"39538-heda-weda-pencho","title":"හැඩ වැඩ පැංචෝ","description":"උත්සාහවන්ත ගෙතුමිට එයාගේ ජීවිතේ අමාරුම ඇඳුම මහන්න වුණ දවසක් ආවා. ගෙතුමි උත්සාහවන්ත ව මේ අමාරු ඇඳුම මැහුවා. ඔයාලා කැමතිද දැනගන්න මොකද්ද මේ ඇඳුම කියලා. ඒ වගේම කොහොමද ගෙතුමි මේ ඇඳුම මැහුවේ කියලා දැනගන්න? ","language":"Sinhala","langCode":"si","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Chammi Iresha"],"illustrators":["Chathurika Jayasooriya"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/39538-heda-weda-pencho"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128596/size3/07263fc4f1cc2f1d1151a56bf7129c7f.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128596/size6/07263fc4f1cc2f1d1151a56bf7129c7f.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77175/size6/ae599a917552bc537d3626f0df04a528.jpg","text":"අවුරුදු ළඟයි,\nගෙතුමිට වැඩ ගොඩා... යි.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77176/size6/3751fdf02e8fd4966913480bed694bbe.jpg","text":"ඒත්... කූරිට කොහොමද ඇඳුමක් මහන්නේ?","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77177/size6/c764eadeaf606772402bab0781a9f311.jpg","text":"මුලින්ම මහපු\nඇඳුම තුනී වැඩියි.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77178/size6/eb5bb092d974ad8faa8c32f6c61348f7.jpg","text":"අනෙත් එක ගොරෝසුයි.\nකූරිට ඇවිදින්න බෑ.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77179/size6/44d97b5ac9f4bf7672d8f5ca24cd802f.jpg","text":"“අවුරුද්දට ගෙදර ඉන්නවා.” කූරි හිතුවා.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77180/size6/543c72d537d9726ee8107ee6b79e5336.jpg","text":"“කූරිට ඇඳුමක් මහනවාමයි.” ගෙතුමි හිතුවා.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77184/size6/d33c8e24bd71d36c9a0f99d07caea116.jpg","text":"ඊළඟ ඇඳුමත් හරි ගියේ නෑ.\nකූරු ඔක්කොම එළියේ.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77183/size6/b001b51c8438a588bd9af25c39e16bdf.jpg","text":"“කූරු නිසා, මට ඇඳුම් ගැළපෙන්නේ නැහැ.”","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77186/size6/06d2652b1c25ba9e6cc0b437acd9e7d4.jpg","text":"ගෙතුමි නිදාගන්නේ නැතිව වැඩ කළා.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77187/size6/26e6ec453f32b96d926ecce8a79df633.jpg","text":"එයා කූරිගේ කූරු වටේට \nලස්සන ගෙත්තමක් කළා.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77188/size6/f9c843199dc34c2cade665477466eeee.jpg","text":"අවුරුදු උත්සවයට හැමෝම ලස්සන ඇඳුම් ඇඳලා.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77189/size6/761be166dc696fbf8e9bdc895ddc71bb.jpg","text":"තරග ගොඩකුත් තිබුණා. තෑගි, කුසලාන ගොඩා... යි.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77190/size6/17ea095fccd4811721674a35440a9a6c.jpg","text":"“ලස්සනම ඇඳුම” \nතරගය දිනුවේ අපේ කූරි...","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77191/size6/dcdde296d74298f2a86ae4824ee9a271.jpg","text":"කැලේ ලොකුම තෑග්ග තමයි උත්සාහවන්තයාට දෙන තෑග්ග.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77192/size6/8cb7b3ea1ea66057fb9cbf00ae7dc0df.jpg","text":"ඒක දිනුවේ... ගෙතුමි.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77193/size6/4ff97c2e6601a4f6ad91072ce7f8aef5.jpg","text":"17/17","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":88}}